Detailed Description

TRA data format definition.

Use the type field to determine which union element to use.

In Octeon 2, the trace buffer is 69 bits, the first read accesses bits 63:0 of the trace buffer entry, and the second read accesses bits 68:64 of the trace buffer entry.
